   - insert
    - json encoded object
    - decode header
    - save
    - reply
 - simple (covers all features)
  - receive json request from simple command line input generator
  - send to 2 tasks, get time and get count
  - join back
  - queue to 2+ sleepers (random sleep)
  - reply
